'''''Legacy'' 16''' is the sixteenth issue of the ''[[Star Wars: Legacy]]'' comic series. The origin of [[Darth Krayt|A'Sharad Hett's]] descending into Darth Krayt is revealed in this issue.

==Publisher's summary==
''Much has been told about the legacy of the [[Skywalker family/Legends|Skywalker family]], but until now little has been said of the legacy of [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]]!''

''If you think you know the whole story, prepare yourself for a shock. In the wake of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], Obi-Wan fought [[Duel on Tatooine (Imperial Period)|a lonely battle]]&mdash;the outcome of which rocks the future of the ''Star Wars'' galaxy!''

''Another layer of the ''Legacy'' mystery is revealed!''

==Plot summary==
{{Plot|comic}}

==Continuity==
A'Sharad Hett's duel with Obi-Wan Kenobi is expanded upon in the young adult novel ''[[The Life and Legend of Obi-Wan Kenobi]]''.

